hasReportedLice.description: True if lice count is included in the report for this week

avgAdultFemaleLice.description: Average adult female lice per fish (this is the lice development stage lice limits target)

hasCleanerFishDeployed.description: Has cleanerfish been used to combat lice this week?

hasMechanicalRemoval.description: Has mechanical removal methods been used to combat lice this week?

hasSubstanceTreatments.description: Has chemical substances, bath or in-feed, been used to combat lice this week?

lat.description: Published location of the site(latitude and longitude in EPSG:4326)

isOnLand.description: True if site is land based, false if at sea

numberOfReportingLocalities.description: Some localities may have submitted a report but still be exempt from including lice count depending on a number of circumstances

localitiesAboveThreshold.description: Above legal threshold for avg adult female lice per fish

totalNumberOfLocalities.description: Total number of loalities for week, fallow and active

escapes.description: List of escapes (from all sites in this summary) this week. Data from Fiskeridirektoratet.

newLocalitiesWithDisease.description: List of new sites with disease (PD or ILA) this week. Sites are filtered.

year.description: Number of new sites with disease (PD or ila) by week, for all weeks the selected year. Sites are filtered.

localitiesAboveLiceLimitAnnual.description: Localities above the lice limit for all weeks in the selected year. Filtered by site filter

avgAdultFemaleLice.description: Average lice count for adult female lice

avgMobileLice.description: Average lice count for lice in mobile stages of development

avgStationaryLice.description: Average lice count for lice in stationary stage of development

maxCombinedNumberOfLice.description: Sum of lice of all types for week with highest combined count

data.description: Value will be null if no temperature has be reported for a week and for all future weeks in year

oneOf.description: Each row represents one week when a site is infected with a disease. All weeks from the infection is registered until the site is declared healthy, gives one row in the export. Weeks where sites are not infected will not have rows in the output. If a site has infections of both ILA and PD for the same week, two rows will be exported for this week.

ruling.description: Whether the infeciton is confirmed 'Påvist' or suspected 'Mistanke'.

fromDate.description: The date the infection or suspected infection was registered.

toDate.description: The date the infection or suspected infection was unregistered. If blank, the site is still considered infected.

municipalityNo.description: The municipality id of the infected site.

municipality.description: The name of the municipality of the infected site.

countyNumber.description: The county id of the infected site.

county.description: The county of the infected site.

lat.description: The latitude of the infected site, EPSG:4326.

lon.description: The longitude of the infected site, EPSG:4326.

productionAreaId.description: Id of the productionarea this site belongs to, according to Produksjonsområdeforskriften

items.description: Wellboat visits at requested site for the requested week.
Lines/tracks for this wellboat. When there is no AIS signal for 1 hour, the track is split

isNoSignal.description: True if this is a track/line with more than 1 hour between the signal. Shown as dashed line in the web gui.

items.description: Points along the track with speed (sog), course (cog) and heading. There is one interval point every hour. Lat/lon is in EPSG:4326.

coordinates.description: Array of coordinates in EPSG:4326 for this track. The track is simplified to 2m accuracy from the raw AIS data.

trackAnalysis.description: Results of a spatial analysis of where the wellboat has been

items.description: Color according to produksjonsområdeforskriften, and validity dates
